ions.\par \par \uc2 Three-quarters of the Iranian funds that passed through \uc2 Binance\uc2  were in a relatively low-profile cryptocurrency called Tron that gives users an option to conceal their identities.\par \par \uc2 The new findings come as the Justice Department is pursuing an investigation into possible money laundering by \uc2 Binance\uc2 . The transactions put the company at risk of falling afoul of U.S. prohibitions on doing business with Iran, lawyers and trade-sanctions experts said. REUTERS\par \par \uc2 CONSUMER SPENDING\par \par \uc2 Shares of \uc2 PayPal\uc2  Fall\par \par \uc2 After Cut in Forecast\par \par \uc2 PayPal Holdings\uc2  shares dropped nearly 2 percent after the digital payments heavyweight lowered its annual revenue forecast, warning of a bleak holiday quarter as consumers cut back on discretionary spends.\par \par \uc2 Decades-high inflation has hit the purchasing power of consumers who also have to contend with the threat of a looming recession.\par \par \uc2 PayPal\uc2  said lower- and middle-income households had started reducing nonessential spending, as they grapple with higher prices of food, energy and gas.\par \par \uc2 The San Jose, California-based company on Thursday cut its 2022 adjusted revenue growth outlook to 10 percent from 11 percent forecast earlier, while also forecasting bleak e-commerce growth in the fourth quarter.\par \par \uc2 That was in line with commentary from the \uc2 National Retail Federation\uc2 , which earlier this week forecast holiday sales, including e-commerce, to grow at a slower pace this year even as retailers offer steep discounts to clear out excess inventory. REUTERS\par \par \uc2 (PHOTOGRAPH BY DADO RUVIC/REUTERS) This article appeared in print on page B2. \par \par \uc2 Document NYTF000020221105eib500052\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw284\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4260\pichgoal600
